The paper proposes a deep learning-based framework for automatically tagging, captioning, and recommending images for review datasets. This involves tasks such as image recognition, natural language processing, and recommendation systems, which are commonly associated with computer vision (cs.CV), computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
